data.description: Are you looking for a gated community with a neighborhood pool, playground, and community events?! Look no further than this adorable home centrally located in Rosedale Place. This home offers an open floor plan with a brick fireplace, large kitchen, and spacious laundry room. The master is remote with an on-suite bath, separate vanities & large whirlpool tub. The backyard is fully fenced, offering more entertainment options for you and your guests. THIS HOME IS MUST SEE!! Schedule your showing today!!
